        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "I think that if the 3rd parameter cannot be null than it won't have null as it's default value.\nThe only one thing that is needed is to edit file Zend\/Translate\/Adapter.php and change line 108 from \n\n$this->setLocale($locale);\n\nto\n\nif ( $locale !== null ) $this->setLocale($locale);"
